    <item>
      <title>印度两省开始计票，莫迪支持率面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/modi-s-support-tested-as-two-indian-provinces-begin-vote-counts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度周二开始在两个北部省份计票，出口民调预测，由于选民担心就业和收入问题，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在这两个省的选票将落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/modi-s-support-tested-as-two-indian-provinces-begin-vote-counts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯签署法律吸引国防公司落户菲律宾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/marcos-signs-law-to-attract-defense-companies-to-philippines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯周二签署了一项法律，旨在吸引外国武器制造商在这个东南亚国家设厂，以发展本土国防工业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/marcos-signs-law-to-attract-defense-companies-to-philippines</guid>
